This product uses data from the UK Sanctions List.

- The UK Sanctions List is published by the Foreign, Commonwealth & Development Office
  (FCDO) under the Sanctions and Anti-Money Laundering Act 2018, and is available as open
  data under the Open Government Licence v3.0. Contains public sector information licensed
  under the Open Government Licence v3.0. © Crown copyright.
  Source: https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/the-uk-sanctions-list
- The data bundled in a published build is generated from the official FCDO UK Sanctions
  List CSV via scripts/build-data.mjs; the version present in a fresh source checkout is a
  small synthetic ILLUSTRATIVE sample, not real designations.

sanctionwise performs INDICATIVE name-match screening against the UK (FCDO) list only. A
match is a POSSIBLE match that requires human verification against the official entry; a
non-match is NOT a clearance. It is not legal, compliance, KYC/AML or sanctions advice, and
is not a substitute for a regulated sanctions-screening process.
